---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Integrazioni & Demo — WebCreator Studio"
  description="Esplora le demo interattive di WebCreator Studio: e-commerce headless con Shopify + Astro, integrazioni CMS e molto altro. Realizzazioni concrete, non solo parole."
  canonical="https://webcreator-studio.it/integrazioni"
>

  <section class="integrazioni-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Integrazioni & Demo</span>
      <h1>Vedi le nostre<br /><em>integrazioni live.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Progetti dimostrativi interattivi costruiti con le stesse tecnologie che
        usiamo per i nostri clienti. Esplora, testa, poi chiamaci.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="demos-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="demos-grid">

        <!-- Shopify Demo — active -->
        <a href="/integrazioni/shopify" class="demo-card">
          <div class="demo-card-badge active">Live</div>
          <div class="demo-card-icon">🛒</div>
          <div class="demo-card-body">
            <h2 class="demo-card-title">Shopify Demo</h2>
            <p class="demo-card-desc">
              E-commerce headless realizzato con Shopify Storefront API e Astro.
              Filtri per categoria, carrello persistente, wishlist e checkout modale —
              tutto interattivo, tutto statico.
            </p>
            <ul class="demo-card-tags">
              <li>Shopify</li>
              <li>Astro</li>
              <li>Headless</li>
              <li>Vanilla JS</li>
              <li>LocalStorage</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <span class="demo-card-cta">Esplora la demo →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- Satispay Demo — active -->
        <a href="/integrazioni/satispay" class="demo-card">
          <div class="demo-card-badge active">Live</div>
          <div class="demo-card-icon">💸</div>
          <div class="demo-card-body">
            <h2 class="demo-card-title">Satispay Demo</h2>
            <p class="demo-card-desc">
              Integrazione Satispay per e-commerce: flusso di pagamento completo con
              QR code, deep link mobile e webhook di conferma. Zero commissioni per il cliente.
            </p>
            <ul class="demo-card-tags">
              <li>Satispay</li>
              <li>Next.js</li>
              <li>REST API</li>
              <li>HMAC</li>
              <li>Webhook</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <span class="demo-card-cta">Esplora la demo →</span>
        </a>

        <!-- WooCommerce — coming soon -->
        <div class="demo-card disabled" aria-disabled="true">
          <div class="demo-card-badge soon">Prossimamente</div>
          <div class="demo-card-icon muted">🛍️</div>
          <div class="demo-card-body">
            <h2 class="demo-card-title muted">WooCommerce</h2>
            <p class="demo-card-desc muted">
              Demo di un negozio WooCommerce headless con Next.js e WooCommerce REST API.
              Gestione prodotti variabili, filtri avanzati e integrazione con i principali
              gateway di pagamento.
            </p>
            <ul class="demo-card-tags muted">
              <li>WooCommerce</li>
              <li>Next.js</li>
              <li>REST API</li>
              <li>TypeScript</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <span class="demo-card-cta muted">In costruzione…</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="integrazioni-cta">
    <div class="container integrazioni-cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2>Vuoi un'integrazione su misura?</h2>
        <p>Connettere Shopify, WooCommerce, Stripe, CMS headless o qualsiasi API
           al tuo sito — lo facciamo ogni giorno.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contatti" class="btn btn-primary">Parliamo del tuo progetto →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .integrazioni-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .integrazioni-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .integrazioni-hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== DEMOS GRID ===== */
  .demos-section {
    padding: 64px 0 80px;
  }
  .demos-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .demo-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.25s, transform 0.25s, background 0.25s;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  a.demo-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: var(--bg3);
  }
  .demo-card.disabled {
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* Badge */
  .demo-card-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .demo-card-badge.active {
    background: rgba(74,158,110,0.15);
    color: #6ab88a;
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,158,110,0.3);
  }
  .demo-card-badge.active::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #4a9e6e;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse-dot 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .demo-card-badge.soon {
    background: rgba(200,176,138,0.1);
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,176,138,0.2);
  }

  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50%       { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.7); }
  }

  /* Icon */
  .demo-card-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .demo-card-icon.muted { filter: grayscale(1) opacity(0.4); }

  /* Body */
  .demo-card-body { flex: 1; }
  .demo-card-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .demo-card-title.muted { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .demo-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .demo-card-desc.muted { color: var(--text-subtle); }

  /* Tags */
  .demo-card-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .demo-card-tags li {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .demo-card-tags.muted li { opacity: 0.5; }

  /* CTA */
  .demo-card-cta {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: auto;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }
  a.demo-card:hover .demo-card-cta { gap: 8px; }
  .demo-card-cta.muted { color: var(--text-subtle); }

  /* ===== BOTTOM CTA ===== */
  .integrazioni-cta {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 64px 0;
    background: var(--bg2);
  }
  .integrazioni-cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .integrazioni-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .integrazioni-cta p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 460px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .demos-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .integrazioni-cta-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .integrazioni-hero { padding: 60px 0 40px; }
    .demos-section { padding: 48px 0 60px; }
  }
</style>
